block content
  .page-header
    .container
      h1  #{blog.title}
        small 联系我们，让我们更好的为您服务
  .blog.article
    .container
      .blog-top.single-top
        .col-md-9.blog-left
          .blog-main.white-bg 
            p.bg #{blog.title}
            p
              | 由 
              a(href='#') Admin
              |  在 #{moment(blog.meta.creatAt).format('YYYY-MM-DD')} 发布
            .blog-main-one
              .blog-one
                .blog-one-left
                  //- img(src=blog.img, alt='')
                p #{blog.article}
              .blog-comments
                ul
                  li
                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-bookmark(aria-hidden='true')
                    a(href='#') #{blog.category.name}
                  li
                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-calendar(aria-hidden='true')
                    p #{moment(blog.meta.creatAt).format('YYYY-MM-DD')}
                  li
                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-user(aria-hidden='true')
                    a(href='#') Admin
            .clearfix          
                  
          .comment-holder.p-30.light-shadow.white-bg        
            ul.comment-list.font-roboto
              li.comment-wrap
                .comment-thumb
                  img.img-responsive(src='/images/t1.jpg', alt='')
                .comment-body
                  a.comment-author(rel='external nofollow', href='#') john smith
                  .comment-content
                    p
                      | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam viverra euismod odio, gravida pellentesque urna varius vitae. Sed dui lorem, adipiscing in adipiscing et, interdum nec metus.
                  header.comment-meta
