                          | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam viverra euismod odio, gravida pellentesque urna varius vitae. Sed dui lorem, adipiscing in adipiscing et, interdum nec metus.
                      header.comment-meta
                        ul.post-meta
                          li
                            i.fa.fa-clock-o
                            | 25 dec, 2016
                          li
                            a(href='#')
                              i.fa.fa-reply
                              | reply
          form.row.form1(method='POST', action="/comment")
            .col-md-6
              .form-group
                label
                  | 怎么称呼
                  i.fa.fa-asterisk
                input.form-control(name='client[name]', type='text')
            .col-md-6
              .form-group
                label
                  | 您的电话
                  i.fa.fa-asterisk
                input.form-control(name='client[tel]', type='tel')
            .col-md-12
              .form-group
                label 有什么疑问呢，在这里写下来
                textarea.form-control(name='client[query]', rows='6')
              .send_result
            .col-md-12
                input.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(value='提交', name='submit', type='submit')
                .clearfix
          
